data.description: The auction for Hubzu property 89916627551 ends 06-27-2023 at 02:00 PM ET. Why wait? Bid on this property now. Visit Hubzu.com to get started. **VACANT** Wonderful single family home oozing with potential, perfect for first-time homeowners or investors. This home was built in 1974 and features 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom, with plenty of living space situated on 1.5 acres.  ***SPECIAL NOTES: (1) This is a CASH ONLY transaction. (2) Seller to pay Taxes, HOA, and Municipal/Utility Liens. (3) The seller has chosen to disclose the reserve price for this property and has set the reserve at $200,755. (4) Bids below the disclosed reserve may be presented to the seller for consideration. (5) Please read the Hubzu disclaimers carefully before placing a bid or submitting an offer. ***
